long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Track your click count to play Bread Winner, an idle clicker game. 

Have you ever wished you could take all the time you spend on the internet and cash it all in? Now you can! In Bread Winner, every click you make across the browser earns money that you put towards baking fresh, digital bread. No opened email, liked facebook post, or clicked article will ever go to waste again. 

Play at breadwinner.app!
